TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
IIF((ISNULL(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1)))=0 OR IS_SPACES(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1)),'0'))=0)
AND (ISNULL(IN_PROVIDER_STREET2_ADDRESS1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_STREET2_ADDRESS1)))=0 OR IS_SPACES(IN_PROVIDER_STREET2_ADDRESS1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_STREET2_ADDRESS1)),'0'))=0)
AND (ISNULL(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1)))=0 OR IS_SPACES(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1)),'0'))=0)
AND (ISNULL(IN_STATE1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_STATE1)))=0 OR IS_SPACES(IN_STATE1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_STATE1)),'0'))=0)
AND (ISNULL(IN_ZIPCODE1) OR IS_SPACES(IN_ZIPCODE1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_ZIPCODE1)))=0 OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_ZIPCODE1)),'0'))=0)
,FALSE,TRUE)

IIF((ISNULL(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1)))=0 OR IS_SPACES(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_STREET_ADDRESS1)),'0'))=0)

AND (ISNULL(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1)))=0 OR IS_SPACES(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1) OR LENGTH(LTRIM(LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_PROVIDER_CITY1)),'0'))=0)
